<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>

    <style>
        /* Basic styling for the page */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Container for the main content */
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Style for the header */
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        /* Style for the profile section */
        .profile {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .profile img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        /* Style for the biography section */
        .bio {
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Style for links */
        a {
            color: #2980b9;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Footer section */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <div class="profile">
            <!-- Replace with your own profile picture -->
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Profile Picture">
            <p class="bio">
                Hi! I'm [Your Name], a passionate photographer and developer. I love capturing moments and turning them into lasting memories through my lens. Besides photography, I have a strong interest in web development and technology. 
                This website is a collection of my work, thoughts, and inspirations. Feel free to explore, and if you like what you see, connect with me!
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2>My Journey</h2>
        <p class="bio">
            My passion for photography started at a young age. Over the years, I've honed my skills in capturing high-quality images, and I've developed an eye for the details that matter. When I'm not behind the camera, you'll find me coding new features for websites or learning about the latest in tech advancements.
        </p>

        <h2>Connect with Me</h2>
        <p class="bio">
            You can find me on these platforms:
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.twitter.com/yourprofile" target="_blank">Twitter</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/yourprofile" target="_blank">Instagram</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yourprofile" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2024 Your Name - All Rights Reserved
    </div>

</body>
</html>
